title: ISic000664. Fragmentary inscription mentioning a likely building
body:

1[---]DHSUAPECUNIAFC

1: orig. DH

Apparatus criticus

Text according to Ampolo and Erdas (2019) L11

English translation

[...] had this set up at his/her own expense.

Italian translation

[...] ha fatto fare a sue spese.
